column4: Developing is the extent to which the district has effectively and fully integrated technology, as defined by the state.
Approaching is the extent to which the district has effectively and fully integrated technology, as defined by the state.
Meets is the extent to which the district has effectively and fully integrated technology, as defined by the state.
Fully integrated is the extent to which the district has effectively and fully integrated technology, as defined by the state.
The district is not required to report the extent to which it has effectively and fully integrated technology, as defined by the state.
